text: Coemansia is a genus of fungi in the family Kickxellaceae. It was circumscribed in 1873. ==Species== *Coemansia aciculifera *Coemansia alma- atensis *Coemansia asiatica *Coemansia bainieri *Coemansia brasiliensis *Coemansia breviramosa *Coemansia ceylonensis *Coemansia erecta *Coemansia furcata *Coemansia guatemalensis *Coemansia interrupta *Coemansia javaensis *Coemansia kamerunensis *Coemansia linderi *Coemansia mojavensis *Coemansia nantahalensis *Coemansia pectinata *Coemansia reversa *Coemansia scorpioidea *Coemansia spiralis *Coemansia thaxteri ==References== Category:Zygomycota genera Category:Fungi incertae sedis
